snippet.title: ZEE.END / Alpha 211014
snippet.description:
Z Ξ Ξ . E N D - multiplayer survival game.

Still no normal zombie game? Because the developers themselves don't play their games and make fundamental gameplay mistakes. Critical bugs and cars flying into space. After 5 minutes of playing, you already have top items. And some release games without a heap of promised content.

We're tired of waiting! We a team of two since the beginning of 2020 have been developing a game that we want to play ourselves. We are people who have played such mods on Arma 2 - dayz and epoch and consider them to be the best in gameplay and atmosphere.

Introducing ZEE.END!

We are looking for funding and cooperation.
Friends! We need any financial support for the development of the project.
Purchase of 3D models and other various assets is required.
For funding or cooperation, please contact us: xxxtlee@gmail.com, temamail@mail.ru

Steam
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1715970/ZEEEND/

Twitch
https://www.twitch.tv/zee__end

More screenshots and information about the game and development:
https://vk.com/zee_end
